    {
      "name": "places/ChIJ2fQZM8hZwokR2cE3VIthTeo/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tSc2MxQTNUSHBHUzFOV2FEWkNYMjR5YzFaM2VIYxAB",
      "relativePublishTimeDescription": "6 months ago",
      "rating": 5,
      "text": {
        "text": "What a fabulous salon. And affordable too!\nI happened in there this am and was treated to an exceptional nail treatment by Co Co. My nails were in rough shape! She did a fantastic job job cleaning them up, adding tips, and an awesome dip power in “Christmas Red”. I highly recommend this salon, and will book again when I return to NYC… 👏👏👏👏👏",
        "languageCode": "en"
      },
      "originalText": {
        "text": "What a fabulous salon. And affordable too!\nI happened in there this am and was treated to an exceptional nail treatment by Co Co. My nails were in rough shape! She did a fantastic job job cleaning them up, adding tips, and an awesome dip power in “Christmas Red”. I highly recommend this salon, and will book again when I return to NYC… 👏👏👏👏👏",
