    {
      "name": "places/ChIJ2fQZM8hZwokR2cE3VIthTeo/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25wNE5ERllUbGRvTm5oMU5FNVFWR1ZvZEZwcU5YYxAB",
      "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago",
      "rating": 1,
      "text": {
        "text": "Within the first 3 minutes of my pedicure with Kiki I was cut so deep I bled and was offered a Red Bull (at 6pm) as a consolation. Proceeded to give me the worst French pedicure I’ve seen that I had to coach/correct through multiple times to which she seemed exasperated by. This is supposed to be a $68 pedicure. Save yourself the embarrassment of walking out when they offer you a laughable discount on an open wound and pedicure that looks like a 6 year old did it.",
        "languageCode": "en"
      },
      "originalText": {
